{
  "stem": "15991.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I think by fleeing to London and going through the experiences I had gone through and looking after my family, it has shaped my life tremendously.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I feel that, due to that, I've become a much better person than I would ever been without that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we were a well-to-do family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I had no responsibilities.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was a very immature person, really, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and not enjoyed the schooling very much and had no real idea of what I wanted to do.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But then, who does at 14, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Still, I really feel that very strongly, that--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It could have, yes, because I've become a better person, maybe.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, with all being-- as a religion, you talked about religion before.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We've all joined-- Andrew and I joined the Ethical Culture and attended regularly.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the children attended regularly, too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "While my son David has not kept this up, Jennifer my daughter has and has become active in Washington and Virginia in Ethical Culture society.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And her husband also is active in Washington society, so I feel it's-- it's done something.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We did try at one point to-- for Jennifer to join a synagogue and take religious instruction there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we weren't too pleased with that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It just didn't feel natural.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We tried to celebrate Hanukkah, tried to keep the holidays, and it just wasn't comfortable.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so we decided to not go along with this and then joined Ethical after that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It means to be very proud of it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From a point-of-view of heritage, [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] I've been to Israel.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I think it's just wonderful what has been done.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
